      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON GUITAR (1) was below best last time at this track (35.57) in a Grade 5, finishing a 12 length sixth. Has already won four times from this draw. Makes strong appeal on best. REGAL JYLE (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 5.5 lengths at Bendigo in a handy 27.87 beating Larni Lou. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Sure to measure up. PAW ZOLTIN (5) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Finished third (30.53) at this track last time making it three minors on end. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Ready to find winning form. MAGIC SCOTCH (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
